  "Description": {
    "English": "Improves the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fuel efficiency</span> of the jetpack's marine jets, reducing the drain on Exosuit life support systems.<br><br>Aqueous compressor units are installed into the jetpack's turbines, bypassing the large energy requirements of underwater ignition.",
